WEBVTT

00:00:27.183 --> 00:00:30.142
Gledao sam u svoj mobitel i razmišljao
kako bih to mogao jednostavno izbrisati.

00:00:30.442 --> 00:00:34.607
Ili bih mogao napraviti nešto
što sam oduvijek želio.

00:00:34.631 --> 00:00:37.622
(Smijeh)

00:00:38.541 --> 00:00:40.750
Odgovorih, "Solomone, 
tvoj email me zaintrigirao."

00:00:40.774 --> 00:00:43.476
(Smijeh)

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:48.476
(Pljesak)

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.920
Igra je započela.

00:00:53.214 --> 00:00:56.175
On odgovori, "Dragi James,
slat ćemo ti Zlato."

00:00:56.199 --> 00:00:57.896
(Smijeh)

00:00:58.302 --> 00:01:01.199
"Zaradit ćeš 10% od svog zlata
koje ćeš distribuirati."